column5: A run down on the days events in HD (You have to put it in 1080 down in the right side of the screen click on the 360 and you can choose the better quality) Had a great time and I can't wait till next year. Congrats to all the winners. <object width="560" height="315"><param name="movie" value="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ql4qI8hFKhY?version=3&hl=en_US&hd=1"></param><param'>http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ql4qI8hFKhY?version=3&hl=en_US&hd=1"></param><param name="allowFullScreen" value="true"></param><param name="allowscriptaccess" value="always"></param><embed src="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ql4qI8hFKhY?version=3&hl=en_US&hd=1" type="application/x-shockwave-flash" width="560" height="315" allowscriptaccess="always" allowfullscreen="true"></embed></object>
Thanks to everyone for driving wide open in a no wake zone and swamping us, hope you enjoyed the day!  (not directed at you, love the vids)
I Can't believe they dont have the blast off at the mouth the harbour. I was in front of the pack would have gotten run over if I had obeyed the no wake zone. A little scary to say the least.
It was a good day .Thanks for the great vid. Dan
